"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932197-Team-GB-Olympics-Molly-Caudery\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GBathlete Molly Caudery broke down in tears and apologised for her failure to bring home a medal from the2024 Olympicsfollowing her shock elimination from the pole vault event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caudery, who had an hour earlier been consoling her team-mate Holly Bradshaw for failing to qualify, was left devastated by her own failure after she could not clear her opening height of 4.55m in the heats.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9705305942102774, \"rank\": 0.019257122832130685, \"text\": \"Holly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Holly_Cunningham\"}, {\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"score\": 0.9917863846297403, \"rank\": 0.0077763704983444685, \"text\": \"Bradshaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old from Truro had been expected to land a gold medal for Team GB and the Truro-born athletics star gave a heartfelt apology live on TV after failing to qualify.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truro\", \"score\": 0.9999939573256814, \"rank\": 3.993850565176329e-06, \"text\": \"Truro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Truro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's totally heartbreaking, not the Olympic experience I was hoping for.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just so sorry to everyone back at home,\\\" Caudery told BBC Sport.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.8659366757413712, \"rank\": 0.15462255965260394, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish I could've done better for everyone and myself of course.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am going to try and learn from this.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's still an Olympic experience and I will take everything I can from it.\\\"\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what went wrong in her pole vault routine, she replied: \\\"It's honestly what I have been asking myself.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt great, I am in the best shape of myself and I had an amazing warm-up.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999952747203, \"rank\": 4.7252202523866245e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.999084710926267, \"rank\": 0.0009161246240651926, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not feel too nervous - I love a big crowd.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For some reason, that I do not know right now, it wasn't my day.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will go and talk to my coach and hopefully figure some things out.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will just use this as an experience, learn from it and try and move on.\\\"\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caudery was highly-fancied to add Team GB's 11th gold medal at the Games after claiming the world indoor title in June, setting a British record at 4.92m.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999459997009859, \"rank\": 0.0005399991566203375, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999984095071711, \"rank\": 1.5892813954304178e-06, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also claimed a bronze medal at the European Championships in June and finishedfifth at last year's World Championships.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But things did not work out for the Cornwall native, while her Team GB colleague Bradshaw, 32, was also eliminated.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2019, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornwall\", \"score\": 0.9999900070262344, \"rank\": 9.993073444855294e-06, \"text\": \"Cornwall\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornwall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cornwall\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999459997009859, \"rank\": 0.0005399991566203375, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"score\": 0.9917863846297403, \"rank\": 0.0077763704983444685, \"text\": \"Bradshaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Layfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Former British 400m runner Katharine Merry described Caudery's exit from the Olympics as the \\\"biggest shock\\\" of the track and field events so far.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9971736634982333, \"rank\": 0.0013825302218650173, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Merry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Merry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Merry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Merry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Molly Caudery has gone over a height of 4.92m [this season] - 4cm higher than anyone else in the world,\\\" Merry said on BBC Radio 5 Live.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BBC Radio 5 Live\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Radio_5_Live\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"She decided to come in at an opening height of 4.55m.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In her pool nobody else entered at that height, everyone else came in at an earlier height.\\\"\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2986,